OL,3,CNeighbour of train worker injured
OL,4,Cduring knife attack praises 'heroic'
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,FThe neighbour of a train worker badly
OL,8,Finjured while trying to protect
OL,9,Fpassengers during a mass stabbing has
OL,10,Falways been called a hero by his
OL,11,Fneighbour in Peckham.
OL,13,FRay Zarb said Samir Zitouni saved "so
OL,14,Fmany people" from death or injury on
OL,15,Fan LNER train from Doncaster to London
OL,16,Fon Saturday night.
OL,18,F"I think the guy's a hero," said Ray.
