OL,3,CNeighbour of train worker injured
OL,4,Cduring knife attack praises 'heroic'
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"He has saved god knows how many
OL,8,Fpeople from either death or serious
OL,9,Finjury.
OL,11,F"That is top, top behaviour and
OL,12,Ftypical of him, I would say very
OL,13,Ftypical of him," Ray explained.
OL,15,FMr Zitouni is a customer experience
OL,16,Fhost and "did not hesitate as he
OL,17,Fstepped forward to protect those
OL,18,Faround him", his employer said.
OL,20,FHe remains in hospital in a stable
OL,21,Fcondition but critically unwell.
