OL,3,CNeighbour of train worker injured
OL,4,Cduring knife attack praises 'heroic'
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"Our thoughts and prayers remain with
OL,8,FSam and his family.
OL,10,F"We will continue to support them and
OL,11,Fwish him a full and speedy recovery."
OL,13,FMr Zitouni's role is customer
OL,14,Fexperience host, which largely
OL,15,Finvolves providing onboard catering.
OL,17,FHis family said in a statement
OL,18,Freleased by LNER: "We have been deeply
OL,19,Ftouched by the outpouring of love and
OL,20,Fkindness shown to Sam, and by the many
OL,21,Fwell wishes for his recovery.
