OL,3,CNeighbour of train worker injured
OL,4,Cduring knife attack praises 'heroic'
OL,5,Cresponse
OL,7,F"The care provided by the hospital and
OL,8,Fthe support from his colleagues at
OL,9,FLNER has been incredible."
OL,11,FAnthony Williams, 32, appeared in
OL,12,Fcourt on Monday, charged with 11
OL,13,Fcounts of attempted murder over
OL,14,FSaturday's mass stabbing in
OL,15,FCambridgeshire and another attack
OL,16,Fhours earlier at a London station.
OL,18,FThe 32-year-old, of no fixed abode,
OL,19,Fwas remanded in custody when he
OL,20,Fappeared at Peterborough Magistrates'
OL,21,FCourt.
